      "text": "A Retrieval Envelope is release-pinned and assembled from authorised lexical results.\nEvery included passage keeps its source, concept, section, locator, and content digest.\nGraph proximity can discover candidates but never proves a factual claim.",
      "uri": "https://fixture.local/retrieval"
    },
    {
      "audience": "public",
      "content_sha256": "7e47cd73d20c6b3309c4e7dcb3095b827ff68a1bf56c5a410a6be2f726b5aad8",
